      "body" : "@HelderPereira I don&#39;t think it should be <i>for this case</i>, since <a href=\"http://grepcode.com/file/repository.grepcode.com/java/root/jdk/openjdk/6-b14/java/util/AbstractCollection.java#AbstractCollection.removeAll(java.util.Collection)\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">the source</a> (line 349) seems to loop through <i>both lists</i> (<code>contains()</code> loops the entire array) and since the <code>singleton</code> is only one element it would be <code>N * 1 = N</code>. However generally it would be <code>N^2</code>."
