    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>There is an easy way of removing all the <code>null</code> values from <code>collection</code>.You have to pass a collection containing null as a parameter to <code>removeAll()</code> method</p>\n\n<pre><code>List s1=new ArrayList();\ns1.add(null);\n\nyourCollection.removeAll(s1);\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
