    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>We can use iterator for the same to remove all the null values.</p>\n\n<pre><code>Iterator&lt;Tourist&gt; itr= tourists.iterator();\nwhile(itr.hasNext()){\n    if(itr.next() == null){\n        itr.remove();\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
