    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I used the stream interface together with the stream operation <strong>collect</strong> and a helper-method to generate an new list.</p>\n\n<pre><code>tourists.stream().filter(this::isNotNull).collect(Collectors.toList());\n\nprivate &lt;T&gt; boolean isNotNull(final T item) {\n    return  item != null;\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
