    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>The <code>Objects</code> class has a <code>nonNull</code> <code>Predicate</code> that can be used with <code>filter</code>.</p>\n\n<p>For example:</p>\n\n<pre><code>tourists.stream().filter(Objects::nonNull).collect(Collectors.toList());\n</code></pre>\n"
