    "question_id" : 4819635,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Mainly I'm using this: </p>\n\n<pre><code>list.removeAll(Collections.singleton(null));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>But after I learned Java 8, I switched to this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>List.removeIf(Objects::isNull);\n</code></pre>\n"
